{"tid":1762291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地真係要嘗試connect廣東人","createTime":"2019-11-29T13:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T03:31:35.000Z","uid":207197,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a2295891f2f578b8610a2e13bb8dd2e2203e3918","tid":1762291,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"作為追求緊民主、人權既香港人<br />\n我地反既係共產黨<br />\n而相對比較多用廣東話既廣東人<br />\n係我地容易d connect既人<br />\n係我地輸出革命既大好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nconnect既方法有好多<br />\n <del>又唔係叫你過去幫手打</del><br />\n第一步就緊係口交先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人有微博、B站等ac<br />\n提醒佢地敵人會玩分化同抺黑，唔好中計<br />\n應對TG既方法等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果佢地keep住持續抗爭<br />\n我地再第二步<br />\n眾籌、外交、文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下條片雖然唔多關事<br />\n但睇完真係覺得廣東人係相對易connect<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FHJroZH5XCg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFHJroZH5XCg&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=22f42cdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FHJroZH5XCg</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！<br />\n香港人 報仇！<br />\n<br />\n廣東人 反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e84915bc85e07d09e47473a27113fd75538ae9e","tid":1762291,"uid":226466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"講咗廣東獨立3 個月<br />\n<br />\n俾人屌風向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c236e34f7f3cc4ee64149aa6ad45969f8efa961","tid":1762291,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:25:07.000Z","msg":"去鳩鐵站派傳單<br />\n睇下你仲敢唔敢一車車送落黎<br />\n消費丫拿屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41008451b0b50735f8f5176897c1f6bee029431","tid":1762291,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"咁好機會輸出革命<br />\n又可以表達香港人關心佢地<br />\n佢地受唔受connect都要試<br />\n<br />\n我地會企係人民個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fb5bcb1b9f5d44a0694ebcf5e6a72f8358bb21","tid":1762291,"uid":207197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e84915bc85e07d09e47473a27113fd75538ae9e","tid":1762291,"uid":226466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"講咗廣東獨立3 個月<br />\n<br />\n俾人屌風向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:29:54.000Z","msg":"獨立又唔好咁快講出口<br />\n佢地唔buy<br />\n一步一步黎<br />\n食下TG佢地慢慢就會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2088cda3e9a60f6fc6dfe05f15dba9c914aa1c04","tid":1762291,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"連新移民都connect唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8398e1e0952b8566f7192f75a880ee8f2ae8b5","tid":1762291,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2088cda3e9a60f6fc6dfe05f15dba9c914aa1c04","tid":1762291,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"連新移民都connect唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:37:21.000Z","msg":"我90後<br />\n中學識個班新移民都係黃<br />\n國際線開多條係支那值得試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59e01a9f6614afae49430863c03e486cdfa4a49","tid":1762291,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:37:38